'''根冠'''（{{lang-en|root cap, calyptra}}）是植物[[根|根]]尖端的數層細胞。根冠的功能包括保護植物根尖的[[分生組織|生長點]]、分泌{{link-en|黏質|Mucilage}}以利根部在土壤中的穿透伸展<ref name=Raven2001>{{cite journal
 | author = Raven, J.A.
 |author2=Edwards, D.
  | year = 2001
 | title = Roots: evolutionary origins and biogeochemical significance
 | journal = Journal of Experimental Botany
 | volume = 52
 | issue = 90001
 | pages = 381–401
 | doi = 10.1093/jexbot/52.suppl_1.381
| pmid=11326045

}}</ref>，並可能參與與土壤微生物的訊息傳遞<ref name=Raven2001/>，另外根冠中的{{link-en|平衡細胞|Statocyte}}與植物感知重力而形成的[[向地性|向地性]]有關<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Kuya|first=Noriyuki|last2=Sato|first2=Seiichi|year=2011|title=The relationship between profiles of plagiogravitropism and morphometry of columella cells during the development of lateral roots of Vigna angularis|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0273117710006101|journal=Advances in Space Research|volume=47|pages=553–562|via=|doi=10.1016/j.asr.2010.09.009|bibcode=2011AdSpR..47..553K}}</ref>。

某些[[寄生植物|寄生植物]]不具有根冠<ref name="isbn1-4067-1634-0">{{cite book |last=Jeffrey |first=Edward Charles |title=The Anatomy of Woody Plants |publisher=Carpenter Press |location=Pomeroy, Ohio |year=2007 |pages= |isbn=1-4067-1634-0 |oclc= |doi= |accessdate=}}</ref>{{rp|138}}。另外許多水生植物(浮萍) 也不具有根冠，而是形成一個稱為根囊（root pocket）的囊狀構造，因其根懸浮於水中，不需穿透土壤，根囊也失去了根冠的保護功能<ref name="Guptagene">{{cite book |last=Gupta|first=P.K.|title=Genetics: Classical to Modern|publisher=Rastogi Publications|location=|year=2007|pages=|isbn=978-8-1713-3896-2|oclc=|doi=|accessdate=|}}</ref>{{rp|2–76}}。

